  "keyFeatures": [
    "Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) for on-chain encrypted balances via Zama fhEVM",
    "Native confidential ERC-20 tokens with euint64 encrypted balances",
    "ERC-20 wrapping into confidential cTokens (e.g., cWETH, cUSDC)",
    "Confidential payments where sender amount is hidden but receiver gets plain ERC-20",
    "Private portfolio management with single-signature batch decrypt",
    "Payment links for merchant fixed-amount confidential payments",
    "Compliance observer model for regulatory access without compromising holder privacy",
    "Client-side TFHE WASM encryption with on-chain input verification"
